Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:01.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:01.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:06.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(450,0)\pos(252,115.5)}第五幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:06.49,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\pos(351,232.5)}將愛奪回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:09.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 再找一找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:14.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也是沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:16.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:18.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 請過來看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:21.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:23.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這井
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:27.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼氣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:28.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是糞便的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:32.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些長耳朵好像把糞便投進井裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:34.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還有件奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:35.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:40.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每家每戶的土間以及廁所的泥土都被挖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:40.45,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}土間：日本傳統民家的生活空間的地板都被柱支撐\N，高於地面。與地面齊高的部分被稱為土間。                     
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:44.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底發生什麼事情了 是長耳朵的伎倆麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:48.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事 他們去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:49.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:56.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚 把那群傢伙全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:59.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把腦袋一個個砍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:12.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,從殺掉的敵軍那裡獲取的有二十份劍和盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:13.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,兩匹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:15.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那些傢伙不會騎馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:18.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在我的計畫中會用上這些馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:20.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,先不管盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:23.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,基本就沒有會使劍的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:27.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那些傢伙卻意外地對制弓充滿熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:31.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 他們在和与一一起在制弓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在一臉愉悅地製造著弓和矢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:38.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像熟練的工匠一樣的狂熱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,先不提劍了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想有長槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,長槍的長度是可以降低士兵的恐懼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:50.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拿起二丈一尺長的槍 哪怕是農民也能殺死武士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:54.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:02:00.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明智光秀那傢伙就是在伏見被農兵給殺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:04.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,活該 金柑頭 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:03.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(450,0)\pos(252,115.5)}第五幕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:09.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是偉大啊 伏見的農兵 百萬年無稅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 信長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:13.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是樂於用壞伎倆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:17.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭本身不過是開戰前的積累的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:22.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在開戰之前所做的一切才是 真正的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:28.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說除了秀吉就再沒有其他人明白其本質了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正奇怪村子裡士兵的屍體都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:38.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是你們收集在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡什麼就拿什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還都沾有血跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:46.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去洗吧 天選之子們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都沾滿了血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:50.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:54.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}屍體的情況還是不要說為妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵的頭都被豐久切掉並埋到墳墓去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,身體則是由信長處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人頭都已經拿去祭奠 上供了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:10.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,身體也好好地拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是噁心的氣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:24.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是硝石丘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:29.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,草土和排泄物以及士兵的屍體混合起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:33.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,再過兩年就能收集硝石了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一向眾他們用過的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:41.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這座後山禁止讓村民進入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定還會有什麼傳染病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那廁所的泥土要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說木炭 連硫磺都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:51.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以暫時就那樣放著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:55.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了吧 把敵人的屍體這樣對待…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:58.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢 這和把他們埋葬起來是一樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:01.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,腐爛 被蟲子啃食最終化為泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是加速這一過程而已 本質是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:10.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把他們的人頭清洗乾淨 排列好 再埋葬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作為人來上供了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在這邊只要合掌祭奠即可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:18.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你嫌棄排泄物髒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是我還是你 如果把腹切開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面也不過是填滿了排泄物的肉袋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:26.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,合掌時祭奠的靈魂 不是在他們的人頭裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:30.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是在這填滿排泄物的身體裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這不合乎道理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:39.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 這些人和我們決定性的差異
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:43.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,並非知識 技術 文化之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是生死觀不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 奧爾米 歐派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要叫錯最後一個字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:56.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺差不多懶得生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:05:01.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火山附近常有的散發著臭味的黃色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像用屁製成的粉末的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,叫硫磺的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道怎麼拿到手麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,額 硫磺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:09.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想要還是應該有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但你想要用來幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別管那麼多 拿一堆過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,借助你們那個什麼機關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:19.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,叫派歐機關是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是十月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:24.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我覺得應該不會白白地給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:25.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死人了 派歐機關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等我征服了五六個國家之後再給你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別管了快給我拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,廁所的泥土 屍體 還有硫磺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:37.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底他們葫蘆裡面賣著什麼藥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾米完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 幾乎都能正中靶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:51.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 弓熟練得很快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們原本就擅長使弓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:59.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使長時間被禁止制弓 碰弓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:04.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從戰爭前還是孩提的時候就已經在使弓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:08.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白啦 我已經明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 抱歉 不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:43.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已經充分認識到最強了 你是最強的弓手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,太浪費矢了 所以住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:49.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,攻入村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓他們有任何一人活著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是奪回村子是還不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣順勢攻入地方官的駐地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後把他斬首了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我從這傢伙那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為何這個村子沒有年輕的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們精靈族一年只產一次子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:17.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在那段時期 年輕的女精靈會被地方官帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 就是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:24.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真心想讓你們這個種族斷子絕孫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:26.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要去把女人小孩給奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:29.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你們才算是擺脫家畜的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:34.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們得去斬了那些奴役你們的人的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這個世界上有正邪之分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:38.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這便是正義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可以對彼世的先輩如此說道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是戰死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為了守護家族而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為了奪回女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為了奪回小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:54.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為了奪回國家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:56.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為了奪回真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:05.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙果然天生的武將
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:10.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,並非大名 而是具備在亂世中武將所必需的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是驅使人沖上戰場的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,狂奔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些長耳朵到哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好像說明天開始搜索附近的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果膽敢包庇他們 我們就連那個村子也給滅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,或許…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我喉嚨好乾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喝水就忍著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,井用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:56.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把糞便投進井裡了 混賬長耳朵們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:09:00.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真想快點把那些傢伙都殺光…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.33,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz349\move(250.8,540,819.9,522,7,1049)}強襲奧爾特軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:15.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:16.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,村子的東面有情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂…漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:29.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓他們逃了 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:39.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然背後有漂流物插手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何也要逮到他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全體準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10.08\move(996,262.5,1035,135,9,2011)}精靈族村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10.73\move(1086,325.5,1110,237,0,2011)}釣魚大會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz8.127\move(1221,502.5,1317,471,9,2011)}豐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs67.5\move(1323,709.5,1449,741,1427,9)}（笨蛋）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(1311,652.5,1452,669,1427,9)}誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(783,706.5,684,795,9,1969)}信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(786,753,672,882,9,1969)}織田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs75\move(828,850.5,792,942,9,2011)}野伏長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:56.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,速度 速度就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:59.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,按著我教你們的來做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:05.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,若是搞砸了不過也就死掉罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:15.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,曾率領二十萬軍隊的我也會淪落到這種田地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有趣啊 這地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,對手不是只有一個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:37.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把他包圍起來剿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:37.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這傢伙到底是在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:51.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,放馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:55.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,開始幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:57.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把車靠緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 喂 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:10.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,會死的喲 大家都死的喲 趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:13.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,準備火矢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就要和這個村子說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,做好覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:23.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要和束縛住你們的這個村子和農奴生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,放矢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的國家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵們都太弱小了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是辛苦我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我年復一年地在想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:03.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼方法可以彌補他們的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:08.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到 我居然要模仿猴子的點子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:15.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是我的墨俁城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:15.18,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}\N註：墨俁城又名“一夜城”。相傳是由織田信長\N的部下豐臣秀吉於永祿九年（1566）一夜間築成。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:25.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 一起射出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:33.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個叫奧爾特的國家現在正處於戰爭中對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:37.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那現在的這些都是留下來守家的衛兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:42.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士氣還有訓練程度都很低
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:45.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的隊伍才不會戰死至最後一兵一卒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要把全部人都當成目標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:53.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殺他個一兩成三四十人剩下的人就會四分五裂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就會夾著尾巴逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以農奴作為對手根本得不到什麼功績
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被殺了反而得不償失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:06.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真可憐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:10.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,況且我們這邊 不管射中哪裡都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:26.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼 快點重整隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:30.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那種小花園柵欄只要突進一次就能破壞它了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有屎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,箭裡有屎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:35.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,水 快用水沖洗 不然會染上破傷風的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒有水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,井裡面全都是糞土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵們帶過來的水也快沒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:53.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就想到這樣而把糞土倒在井裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個村就是一個巨大的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:57.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:03.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,並 並不是打算放棄這個村莊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:07.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,準備 射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是開玩笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:15.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要自亂陣型 我們在人數上有絕對的優勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要冷靜下來就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:36.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這鬼叫聲 就像是猴子叫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是人能發出的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:49.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把首領的人頭留下 變成我的戰功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:05.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙 豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:19.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在最好的時機殺進來 最好的時機取下首領人頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,擊潰對方的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:25.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個為戰爭而生的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:34.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,贏 贏了 贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:37.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過要把地方官的城池也攻下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老說攻下來攻下來 你想好什麼方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打贏的時候就應該追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,追擊到他們的根基
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:03.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,從小就教育我要打就要打到對方完全滅亡為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,父親和叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,另一位叔叔和另一位叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:12.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺還有曾爺爺都說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:16.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真討人厭的家族啊 你們家太古怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜冷靜 我有一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:27.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在逃跑的士兵們 應該都目睹了地獄的光景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:31.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 都四散開來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 又是 這又是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:49.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也有糞土塗在上面 這都是些什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是那個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事 這種做法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:08.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這種做法與武士之道相違背啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:10.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得太卑鄙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:14.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙？武士之道？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼是「卑鄙」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,正所謂兵不厭詐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一你還是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:28.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論平氏 源氏 鐮倉還是笨蛋哥哥都是些天真的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:33.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就閉嘴跟著我說的去做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:42.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記那種人吧 那種怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家都到齊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵們還沒回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人都沒回嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,定期聯絡也中斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是單純的村民出逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:10.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我們派出了這裡幾乎所有的士兵真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:14.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾特本國的戰況也越來越糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:18.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在需要對所有的殖民地進行掠奪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:19.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅是精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:23.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的亞人什麼時候會爆發都說不准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:26.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都只派出一小隊人馬的話只會深陷泥潭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:29.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,必須一次把他們打趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:33.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在精靈族導致所有的殖民地叛亂之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:38.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不消滅一兩個村莊來殺雞儆猴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:45.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,關鍵時候 可能還要吊死幾個那些女性的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:50.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,執廳大人 士兵們 士兵們歸來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,開門 開門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:04.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本隊伍現在正對各個村莊進行巡邏壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:08.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我們回來進行中途的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:11.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,開門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容不要停 趕快進去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:24.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑 慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,報告 報告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎樣了 果然發生叛亂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:37.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:40.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流物 精靈族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:43.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱 都動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓走的女人都在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:00.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,塔 在塔裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:03.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:08.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵們 我的 我的士兵們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:13.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 雖然有點可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:18.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都死了 剩下的都在樹林裡被与一到處追殺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:25.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,安心吧 到最後你們都會開開心心地一起和糞土混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:30.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後大家都轉生很優質的火藥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:36.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:45.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我投降 我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:45.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:48.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:50.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經把刀扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不殺手無寸鐵之人為戰場的鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,砍下屈服之人的頭為戰士的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,救出女人是最優先的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:06.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:15.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:17.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:36.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:40.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城裡的人都是糞土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:46.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要斬草除根
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:54.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殺光這個城裡的所有士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:03.77,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your way 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:03.77,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开拓你的道路 向着拂晓之空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:08.02,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:08.02,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:12.99,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滾る心に刃と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:12.99,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}灼热翻腾的心中之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:20.12,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}無に成る大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:20.12,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举心无旁骛的大义之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:31.59,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}陽炎は揺れるシンフォニー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:31.59,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}热浪就如晃荡的交响乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:41.60,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}その声　響く三日月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:41.60,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那歌声 在新月之夜下荡漾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:44.94,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}こんなにくべる炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:44.94,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:47.40,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明けぬ夜は無いと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:47.40,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在永不破晓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:51.44,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生を叫ぶ衝動 輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:51.44,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呼喊生存的冲动 闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:56.61,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your way 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:56.61,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开拓你的道路 向着拂晓之空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:00.91,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:00.91,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:05.66,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滲む痛み引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:05.66,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与被染红的痛楚一同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:12.75,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果てない今日を踏んだ大地へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:12.75,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冲破无尽的今日 迈向新大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:19.97,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}栄光を歌う peace at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:19.97,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}歌颂荣光 终归和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:24.10,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}更なる大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:24.10,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举更为雄壮的大义之旗
